{"tid":1382933,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"化學燒傷處理方法！(二級燒傷)","createTime":"2019-07-29T14:53:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T17:18:29.000Z","uid":191275,"like":53,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"ab018daf1b91978c5d10b0b77c9422e49c734f19","tid":1382933,"uid":191275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T14:53:14.000Z","msg":"朋友之前試過二級化學燒傷 <br />\n佢亦都係醫護人員 ！<br />\n想同大家分享之前康復經歷<br />\n唔知有無用 希望幫到大家<br />\n<br />\n1. 一開始既時候會皮膚紅哂 過左6-12個小時後會開始生水皰 (blister / bullae) <br />\n水皰有機會會生到好大 會好痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同今日睇既相差不多<br />\n<br />\n唔洗驚 要用生理鹽水同gauze輕輕抹 定時做消毒<br />\n千祈唔好用酒精或其他！<br />\n會乸到仆街 亦會延誤傷口埋口<br />\n<br />\n2. 當水皰爆左 繼續用生理鹽水每日抹洗傷口 <br />\n要用油布敷！一定要用油布！叫jelonet paraffin gauze!!<br />\n藥房屈臣氏都有得賣 <br />\n每日更換 防止細菌感染<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bmm6s6s.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fbmm6s6s.png&h=18e7b06b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3. 當然如果係三級燒傷就要睇醫生 有機會要做手術 <br />\n建議去有燒傷中心嘅醫院<br />\n威爾斯嘅燒傷中心係香港最好嘅！建議去嗰到<br />\n<br />\n4. 當傷口癒合後要揸除疤膏 <br />\n建議大家買專業嗰種<br />\n朋友係醫院燒傷中心買呢種<br />\n傷口疤痕去得非常理想<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/07/29/224034_8051bdbeeb8ba76b0f47966bb44998c0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F07%2F29%2F224034_8051bdbeeb8ba76b0f47966bb44998c0.png&h=d7a9372a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有咩問題可以問下<br />\n我嘗試解答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb4462bea49f1a556882fac549a64f53ea38e3c9","tid":1382933,"uid":191275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T14:53:59.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"170f595a34921dc3768ce300267ca9cdcdf45c6e","tid":1382933,"uid":191275,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T14:55:00.000Z","msg":"不過以上方法只係二級化學燒傷嘅處理方法<br />\n如果更嚴重一定要睇醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ad6d63f5be64bdb3957bce2e1263c5e138c268f","tid":1382933,"uid":13343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T14:55:11.000Z","msg":"幫推求fact chrck"},{"pid":"b1f90ada915a01b7c0faaeb7fe9daf593a3debce","tid":1382933,"uid":54125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T14:58:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1bff46208892bf5b09b819b2875cc7ffb97f65ce","tid":1382933,"uid":204835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T14:59:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2518e0f194650976782c24327f75f96a9374cfd2","tid":1382933,"uid":191275,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T15:00:07.000Z","msg":"威爾斯燒傷中心係最齊設施<br />\n同醫生最專業！建議去嗰到"},{"pid":"02eedf35208abfc41ce216759e8fcf093a781b9d","tid":1382933,"uid":199893,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T15:01:11.000Z","msg":"重要嘢要push"},{"pid":"ad809222d1e5e9171456011b603760eaf5e7c15f","tid":1382933,"uid":191275,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T15:02:52.000Z","msg":"唔洗同人講點整親！<br />\n化學燒傷好多原因㗎！"},{"pid":"ea288de3882c5fcf35a1bc3efc833adeda0bcfde","tid":1382933,"uid":266635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T15:04:55.000Z","msg":"盪傷用寶膚寧好得，萬寧，同仁堂有售。家居必備"},{"pid":"6dd1be42b130f9f4e570f0e4f1f26bf04d68d89b","tid":1382933,"uid":125453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T15:05:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hk